# Placement Preparation Tracker

A web-based application that helps students organize and monitor their placement preparation journey. The platform allows users to track DSA problems, contests, aptitude progress, interview notes, goals, and learning analytics in one place.

## Features

* User Authentication
* DSA Problem Tracker
* Contest Performance Tracker
* Aptitude Progress Management
* Interview Notes Manager
* Goal Setting & Tracking
* Daily Streak System
* Analytics Dashboard



